choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for this week.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Monday - Breakfast: Oatmeal with fresh fruit and nuts (excluding almonds, pistachios, or cashews) 
Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cucumber, tomato, and a vinaigrette dressing 
Dinner: Baked salmon with roasted vegetables (carrots, broccoli, zucchini) 
Snack: Apple slices with almond butter 
Tuesday - Breakfast: Greek yogurt with fresh fruit and nuts (excluding honey or garlic) 
Lunch: Turkey sandwich on whole wheat bread with lettuce, tomato, and mustard 
Dinner: Grilled tofu with roasted vegetables (carrots, broccoli, zucchini) 
Snack: Rice cakes with hummus 
Wednesday - Breakfast: Smoothie bowl with mixed berries, banana, and almond milk
